description: Demolition of existing warehouse (9,625sqm) & the erection of a part 2,3,4,5 & 6 storey building comprising 209 flats (99x1,63x2,44x3, 3x4) and 3xlive/work units (299sqm)together with offices (469sqm) and associated basement car parking for 167 vehicles and the provision of external landscape.
